America's now rebuilding
our aging nuclear arsenal.

16:06.185 --> 16:09.720
<i>Now, the Pentagon wants to spend
hundreds of billions of dollars</i>

16:09.822 --> 16:12.956
<i>on new warheads and new
vehicles to carry them.</i>

16:13.058 --> 16:15.358
<i>But this effort isn't just expensive,</i>

16:15.461 --> 16:18.528
it could actually be a threat
to our global security.

